draw_text(info2_x, info2_y, "Volkmusik is the common umbrella designation of a\nnumber of related styles of traditional folk music from the\nAlpine regions of Germany, Austria, Switzerland,\nSlovenia and South Tyrol. It tends to be dialect-heavy\nand invokes local and regional lifestyles and traditions,\nparticularly those of the Alpine farmers and peasants.\nThe instrument volksmusik is most known for is the\naccordion, invented in Germany in the early 1820s.");